      <title>超过一半的英国人感觉比五年前更穷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/more-than-half-of-people-feel-poorer-than-they-did-five-years-ago-survey-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究发现，超过一半（53%）的人现在感觉比五年前更贫穷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/more-than-half-of-people-feel-poorer-than-they-did-five-years-ago-survey-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 06:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
