    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚选举前改组高级部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-reshuffles-senior-ministers-ahead-of-upcoming-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 自 2022 年上任以来首次进行重大内阁改组，对移民和住房等重要职位的领导层进行了调整，他正在为未来 10 个月内必须举行​​的激烈选举做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-reshuffles-senior-ministers-ahead-of-upcoming-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨未能推动德国经济起飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/germany-economy-olaf-scholz-is-failing-to-engineer-a-liftoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国无法实现有意义的增长，给其经济的长期前景和总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导下的三个执政党的政治希望蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/germany-economy-olaf-scholz-is-failing-to-engineer-a-liftoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾能源部称网站遭黑客攻击并被篡改</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/philippines-energy-department-says-website-was-hacked-defaced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾能源部表示，正在调查周六其一个网站遭到黑客攻击的情况，并已下线该网站以修复系统漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/philippines-energy-department-says-website-was-hacked-defaced</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 02:08:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、日本、韩国希望在美国投票前巩固安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国、日本和韩国在东京举行了一次罕见的会议，签署了联合军事训练协议，寻求在11月美国选出下一任总统之前锁定安全合作成果并提升军事联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国财政大臣里夫斯详述“破碎不堪”的英国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/uk-chancellor-reeves-to-detail-a-broke-and-broken-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将在周一的演讲中描绘英国公共财政的严峻形势，她将陷入反对党和本党内部批评者的夹缝之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/uk-chancellor-reeves-to-detail-a-broke-and-broken-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺解雇 Gensler，聘请“热爱”加密货币的人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/trump-pledges-to-fire-gensler-pick-regulators-who-love-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，如果他重返白宫，他将解雇美国证券交易委员会主席并选择对加密货币友好的监管机构，以吸引虚拟货币爱好者并利用该行业在政治舞台上日益增长的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/trump-pledges-to-fire-gensler-pick-regulators-who-love-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯测试“怪异”标签，抨击特朗普和万斯的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/harris-tests-out-weird-label-in-attack-on-trump-vance-rhetoric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在总统乔·拜登退出总统竞选后的首次筹款活动中，称唐纳德·特朗普及其竞选搭档J·D·万斯的言论“奇怪”，这一举动延续了她上任以来民主党人发起的攻击路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/harris-tests-out-weird-label-in-attack-on-trump-vance-rhetoric</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈兰致命空袭可能引发以色列严厉报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/deadly-strike-in-golan-triggers-threat-of-harsh-israeli-payback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列占领的戈兰高地发生火箭弹袭击，造成 12 名儿童死亡，20 多名儿童受伤，这引发了人们对以色列和黎巴嫩真主党武装组织之间战斗急剧升级的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/deadly-strike-in-golan-triggers-threat-of-harsh-israeli-payback</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 19:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班押注特朗普重返欧盟，增强其破坏者角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/orban-bets-on-trump-s-return-to-supercharge-role-as-eu-disruptor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班提出了新世界秩序的愿景，中国的支持和唐纳德·特朗普可能重返白宫，进一步增强了他在欧盟内部的叛徒角色。他甚至暗示了欧盟以外的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/orban-bets-on-trump-s-return-to-supercharge-role-as-eu-disruptor</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
